## How to read it

- `privacy_decision.reason` explains *why* the effective privacy was computed as it was.
- `model_routing_decision.reason` shows the selected profile, provider, task, privacy, and any gating suffix (`external_blocked` or `cloud_escalation_needs_confirmation`).
- `citation_report.results[*].is_valid` is `chunk_exists ∧ hash_matches ∧ in_retrieved_context` — the citation grounding gate.
- `metrics.latency_ms` is wall-clock for the entire 11-node pipeline.
- `errors` is normally empty; any unexpected exception during `generate_answer` lands here instead of crashing the run.
